summary: This is an email notification from a DOJ system indicating a voice message was received on August 16, 2019, with an attached audio file. The document appears to be a system-generated notification of a communication, but the content of the voice message itself is not provided in the text.

events.title: Voice Message Received
events.description: A voice message was received and logged by the DOJ system, generating an email notification with an attached audio file.

keyFacts: A voice message was received by the DOJ on August 16, 2019, at 3:26:06 PM.
The message was processed through a DOJ email system (voip.usa.doj.gov).
The audio file was attached to the email notification as '20190816_152606.wav'.
The sender/name of the voice message caller is listed as 'unavailable'.
This document is a system-generated notification, not the content of the voice message itself.
